  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Drought Response through Provision of Integrated Water Sanitation and Hygiene (WASH) Promotion Services</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In this project, IOM is scaling up water, sanitation and hygiene (WASH) interventions in rural and pre-urban areas with the objective of saving lives, averting disaster, and improving access to clean water, sanitation and hygiene promotion services for communities living in these areas. This intervention is also expected to reduce further displacement, promote dignified, safe, and secure living conditions for children and women who are exposed to protection risks when accessing limited water resources.</narrative>
  </description>
